  "description": "Set up composite TypeScript configuration across the monorepo. Add \"composite\": true to root tsconfig.base.json and add \"references\" array pointing to each package. Create per-package tsconfig.json files with \"composite\": true and \"declarationMap\": true. This enables incremental builds and proper cross-package type checking via Turborepo.",
